Selenis Leyva https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Selenis_Leyva 0 Selenis Leyva (born May 26, 1972) is a Cuban-born American actress. She is known for her role as Gloria Mendoza in the Netflix comedy-drama series Orange Is the New Black. Selenis_Leyva ( born May_26_,_1972 ) is a_Cuban-born_American_actress .
